<div id="Layer1" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2"> <p align="left"><font class="atitulohistoria"><b> Burro C&atilde;o</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeautores"><b> Ant&oacute;nio Torrado</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>escreveu</b></font></p><p align="left"><font class="anomeilustrador"> <b>Cristina Malaquias</b></font><br><font class="aprofissao"><b>ilustrou</b></font></p></td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20">&nbsp;</td><td width="50%"> <img align="right" border="0" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer2" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Era uma vez um burro de trabalho, daqueles que carregam o dobro do seu peso, de casa para o mercado e do mercado para casa. Mais esfor&ccedil;ado burro n&atilde;o havia.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O dono pouco lhe ligava.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer1','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer3" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> Alimentava-o, dava-lhe cama na <A class="alink" href="#" onMouseOver="stm(Text[30],Style[0])" onMouseOut="htm()">estrebaria</a> e uma chibatada ao descair, uma vez por outra, sobretudo quando o burro se atrasava pelos caminhos tortuosos da serra.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Nem uma festa nas orelhas, que lhe sacudisse as moscas, nem uma palavra de reconhecimento, ao fim de um dia de canseiras. Nada.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer2','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer4" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O burro sentia-se. Achava-se, como se compreende, digno de maior apre&ccedil;o.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E mais se sentia quando reparava que o dono era s&oacute; mimos e afagos para os cachorrinhos que a cadela da quinta dera &agrave; luz.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer3','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer5" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Os cachorros mordiscavam a bainha das cal&ccedil;as do homem e ele ria. Lambiam-lhe as m&atilde;os e a cara e ele ria. Saltavam-lhe &agrave; frente, a ponto de o fazerem trope&ccedil;ar, e ele ria.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- N&atilde;o &eacute; justo - pensava o burro.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer4','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer6" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%"> - Os canitos n&atilde;o alombam com o meu carrego, n&atilde;o puxam a carro&ccedil;a, n&atilde;o aguentam com o meu dono &agrave;s costas e ele faz-lhes festinhas, brinca com eles e enternece-se com os disparates e traquinices dos bichos, como nunca o vi t&atilde;o manso assim.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E era verdade.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer5','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer7" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Se quero receber alguma festa ou prova de simpatia do meu dono, estou a ver que tenho de proceder da mesma maneira - continuou a pensar o pobre do burro.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E assim fez.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer6','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer8" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Na manh&atilde; seguinte, quando o dono o acordou, para atrel&aacute;-lo &agrave; carro&ccedil;a, o burro come&ccedil;ou aos saltos e aos zurros, que, segundo ele, imitavam os latidos dos cachorrinhos.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O dono ficou parvo:
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Que mosca te mordeu, malandro?
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">E foi buscar o chicote.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer7','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer9" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O burro corria atr&aacute;s dele. Dava-lhe dentadas nas cal&ccedil;as, lambia-lhe a cara e at&eacute; tentou p&ocirc;r-lhe as patas nos ombros. O homem caiu ao ch&atilde;o.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">O burro zurrava, abanando a cauda e dando saltinhos, &agrave; roda do dono.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer8','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer10" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">- Este burro endoideceu - gritou o homem, levantando-se. - Espera l&aacute; que j&aacute; te ensino a ganhares ju&iacute;zo.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Deu-lhe tal desanda que, n&atilde;o tivesse a mulher do dono, a certa altura, tirado o cabo do chicote das m&atilde;os do marido, esta hist&oacute;ria tinha tido ainda um fim mais triste do que, de facto, teve.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer9','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="65%"> <img align="right" src="../../../images/Avancar.jpg" border="0" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','show');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','hide')" width="20" height="20"></td></tr></table></div><div id="Layer11" style="position:absolute; visibility: hidden; left:120px; top:180px; width:280px; height:320px"> <table width="100%" height="320" border="0"><tr> <td height="300" colspan="2" valign="top"> <font size="3" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#666666"><b> <div align="normal" style="line-height: 150%">
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">Nem todas as hist&oacute;rias podem acabar bem. Esta acaba com o burro preso &agrave; manjedoira, derreadinho da sova, e a mulher do dono a cuidar-lhe das feridas, com emplastros e unguentos.
</div><div align="normal" style="text-indent:16;line-height: 150%">V&aacute; l&aacute;, que podia ser pior.</div></b> </font> </td></tr><tr> <td width="50%" height="20"> <img align="left" border="0" src="../../../images/voltar.jpg" onClick="MM_showHideLayers('Layer11','','hide');MM_showHideLayers('Layer10','','show')" width="20" height="20"></td><td width="35%"><a href="imprimir.pdf" target="_blank"> <img src="../../../images/impre.jpg" align="left" border="0" width="20" height="20"></a><a href="javascript:MM_openBrWindow('../../../pop_votar.aspx?Mes=10&Dia=29','','menubar=no,width=270,height=170')"><img src="../../../images/votar_over.gif" align="right" border="0" width="67" height="20"></a></td></tr></table></div> 
